 enables crash recovery via replay\n\u2022 Task queues \u2014 how work is routed to workers\n\nMental model: durable brain + history; your node executors become Activities.","fontSize":15,"fontFamily":5,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Core concepts:\n\u2022 Workflow \u2014 orchestration code (deterministic): what runs next, branches, waits\n\u2022 Activity \u2014 side effects: HTTP, Composio, sandboxed JS, DB writes\n\u2022 Worker \u2014 polls Temporal, runs workflows + activities\n\u2022 Event history \u2014 durable log; enables crash recovery via replay\n\u2022 Task queues \u2014 how work is routed to workers\n\nMental model: durable brain + history; your node executors become Activities.","autoResize":false,"lineHeight":1.25,"version":337,"index":"c0Hj"},{"angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":["QcEHqfurDKPyJIVCHxIfc"],"frameId":null,"seed":1058693037,"versionNonce":786063853,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1784708679956,"link":null,"locked":false,"type":"ellipse","id":"iOYFMY1fm5E9ppqJoWTqd","x":-4984.800993484607,"y":10460.102666971017,"width":40,"height":40,"strokeColor":"#22C55E","backgroundColor":"#22C55E","roundness":null,"version":337,"index":"c0Hk"},{"angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":["QcEHqfurDKPyJIVCHxIfc"],"frameId":null,"seed":627827213,"versionNonce":443653197,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1784708679956,"link":null,"locked":false,"type":"text","id":"CkFB87LeaXaAVsMM-rpeQ","x":-4973.800993484607,"y":10470.102666971017,"width":160,"height":20,"strokeColor":"#FFFFFF","backgroundColor":"transparent","roundness":null,"text":"I","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":5,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"I","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25,"version":337,"index":"c0Hl"},{"angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth"