fter an unlucky lease expiry.\nOnly a genuine worker-killer racks up 5. And auto-retries never inflate the counter:\neach retry is a NEW message starting at delivery 1.","fontSize":17,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Why 5? A healthy message is delivered once \u2014 twice after an unlucky lease expiry.\nOnly a genuine worker-killer racks up 5. And auto-retries never inflate the counter:\neach retry is a NEW message starting at delivery 1.","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25,"index":"c0SB"},{"id":"FxbhbHNx3oLrBfVVb2m6r","type":"text","x":7605.718824618798,"y":12360.071511575481,"width":2578.68,"height":22.5,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#495057","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"seed":568529581,"versionNonce":1389941997,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1784708679985,"link":null,"locked":false,"version":95,"text":"User sees a failed run with a Retry button instead of an eternal spinner. Retry mints a fresh message \u2014 if the cause was a since-fixed deploy, the run continues; if the job is truly poison, it's back in the DLQ five crashes later, evidence intact.","fontSize":18,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"User sees a failed run with a Retry button instead of an eternal spinner. Retry mints a fresh message \u2014 if the cause was a since-fixed deploy, the run continues; if the job is truly poison, it's back in the DLQ five crashes later, evidence intact.","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25,"index":"c0SC"},{"id":"k76xjkAWzQKne148_srq0","type":"rectangle","x":7545.718824618798,"y":12540.071511575481,"width":2760,"height":900,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#adb5bd","backgroundColor":"#f8f9fa","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":{"t