5407299,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1784721652853,"link":null,"locked":false,"index":"c0s4","version":99,"type":"text","x":13379.627374809386,"y":9335.176721296017,"width":756.8000000000001,"height":40,"text":"3 \u2014 The decision: Amazon RDS for PostgreSQL","originalText":"3 \u2014 The decision: Amazon RDS for PostgreSQL","fontSize":32,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},{"id":"zzu4jhxW0cxF8QUmnwHSM","angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"seed":789413699,"versionNonce":1610889187,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1784721652853,"link":null,"locked":false,"index":"c0s5","version":99,"type":"text","x":13379.627374809386,"y":9390.176721296017,"width":2500,"height":157.5,"text":"1. Relational Postgres is mandatory \u2014 same-version FKs + uniqueness stay in the DB.\n2. AWS is home \u2014 SQS is already the queue; do not split clouds.\n3. Distributed SQL / sharding are premature \u2014 peak is ~1000 small txns/s, not \u201cone machine is full.\u201d\n4. Aurora is optional luxury \u2014 pay more for nicer HA later if needed.\n5. RDS is the cost/simplicity default that still speaks full PostgreSQL (and CDC later).\n\nLocked: one region \u00b7 one writer \u00b7 managed by AWS \u00b7 planning size ~2 vCPU / 4 GB.","originalText":"1. Relational Postgres is mandatory \u2014 same-version FKs + uniqueness stay in the DB.\n2. AWS is home \u2014 SQS is already the queue; do not split clouds.\n3. Distributed SQL / sharding are premature \u2014 peak is ~1000 small txns/s, not \u201cone machine is full.\u201d\n4. Aurora is optional luxury \u2014 pay more for nicer HA later if needed.\n5. RDS is the cost/simplicity default that still speaks full PostgreSQL (and CDC later).\n\nLocked: one region \u00b7 one writer \u00b7 